description.narrative: The joint Government-UN Youth Houses Initiative has been further strengthened by adding new components to an integrated package of specialised services for youth, securing new partnerships at government and civil society levels and expanding geographical coverage from two to six districts. The first Master's degree programme for preparation of youth work managers and youth policy specialists in Azerbaijan has been officially launched in six local universities. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:10/02/2020
